Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.46,0:01:17.13,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to school now!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.08,0:01:19.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.98,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's April.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.46,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a 2nd year student.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.02,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What class are Chizu and Ayane in?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.44,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.78,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We still have two years until graduation. Let's make the most of them!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.53,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That was more nerve wracking than I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.67,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We were really lucky, weren't we?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.75,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.13,0:02:36.56,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo and Ekko are in our class too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.20,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,And so is Joe!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.22,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.14,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough of him?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.14,0:02:47.68,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been really lonely if we weren't in the same class...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.48,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm dreaming right now!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring a CD tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.15,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.89,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.50,0:03:21.40,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys! This girl's name is Sawako Kuronuma. \NYou guys can call her Sadako if you'd like!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.65,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like things are still the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.60,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Line up in the hallway! It's time for the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, let's make this a good year!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.05,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamt that I was going out with her!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Akihiko's concert was so amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.91,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're too spread out! Compact yourselves!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.29,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chigusa is in class C.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.01,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.87,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're all in the same class again!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.71,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Funny how that works.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.61,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like you know something I don't?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.37,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Onto more important business...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What? You didn't give the chocolates to him?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.72,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,But you spent all that time making them! Why not?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.88,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Something definitely happened on Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.79,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been so awkward and strained since then.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.37,0:04:33.50,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that she's finally come \Nto realize how she feels about him...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.96,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,But then again...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.28,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What are those two doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.69,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,We had spring break and holidays and everything!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.17,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.22,0:04:53.47,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, love is all about timing.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.55,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.24,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's already rejected me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.70,0:05:16.18,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's been bothering me since that day...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.30,0:05:24.78,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that Kazehaya doesn't like dating?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.84,0:05:31.15,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Please work hard at both your academics \Nand your extracurricular activities.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.15,0:05:37.32,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it possibly be that he already has someone he likes?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.38,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can understand
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.38,0:05:47.46,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,what Kurumi meant now when she said that she wished \NKazehaya could just remain everyone's beloved Kazehaya
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.36,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,instead of being someone's.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.36,0:05:53.20,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have any hidden meaning to them?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.04,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.90,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,and he even said good morning to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.90,0:06:03.22,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,All of that is like a dream come true, and yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.21,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.66,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't forget what it was like when it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.28,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be greedy
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.78,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,to want more of that, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.77,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I would have hidden intentions then, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Akihiko's final costume was amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It made everyone go crazy!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako! Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.42,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You know me?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we're sitting next to each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kento Miura.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.69,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.20,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! A-OK!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.43,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,So people like this really exist.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.07,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,So you do have eyebrows!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.70,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He's so close!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.75,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,You look kinda scary now.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.41,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.41,0:07:20.43,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,You'll give yourself wrinkles!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.46,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Poke, poke.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.85,0:07:27.12,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Scary.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.12,0:07:31.34,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's hurry up and pick our committee members.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.34,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with class rep...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.60,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Should I pick?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.60,0:07:45.06,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny, meeny, miny, mo. With whom should I go?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.65,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't the time for me to be scared!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.91,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to do it...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.28,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,I could do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.41,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, that was close.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.94,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I almost took away someone's fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You sure, Kento?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.74,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Won't I get lots of attention that way?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.88,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll never get as much attention as me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.88,0:08:12.15,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that guy next to Sawako's pretty bold.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.60,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,A new student, huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.19,0:08:19.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I nominate Kuronuma for class life rep.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.37,0:08:24.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma's really good at taking care of the flowers.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're always taking care of the flowerbeds for us!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.45,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.54,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.77,Italics,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.35,Italics,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,She can smile.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.85,Default,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too much, I'll help too!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.59,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.15,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the atmosphere rep will be...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.88,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Jonochi! Congrats!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, rise!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.50,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.43,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,That might be good too—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.40,Alt,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Miura!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.34,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.36,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.36,0:09:40.10,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all you need to know about being \Nclass rep and respecting your homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.98,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.98,0:09:46.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle. That's why I told you not to do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.80,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Hassles can be fun, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Always with that positive attitude.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.57,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,Hatsure.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.08,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,You can go on without me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.48,Default,Hatsure,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was gonna wait?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.22,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you guys tomorrow!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.17,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.57,0:10:14.23,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to the library. Good luck, Sawako!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.94,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It was hilarious!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.53,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.48,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going home now, Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.81,0:10:39.15,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm going to stay for a bit and \Nplant some seeds in the flowerbeds.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.66,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.86,0:10:43.69,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.41,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.91,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.71,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.58,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.50,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ryu!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.74,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Today was just the opening ceremony and you already have practice?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.54,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.83,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, has the date been decided yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Databin?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,The date for Toru's wedding!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.94,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.90,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,When was it again?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.27,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask your dad next time I see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.91,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.88,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.45,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you guys have a tournament coming up?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.29,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,The spring tournament is soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go to Koshien if you win?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.54,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,That's summer.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.23,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,The spring tournament is more of a practice run.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.14,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's still good if you win, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.64,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.41,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.76,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.87,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come over for ramen tonight!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.64,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.64,0:12:58.46,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.47,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.50,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean for what? Dividing the classes!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.38,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what I said to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.97,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,As if I bothered listening to all of your requests.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.20,0:13:15.52,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happen 2nd and 3rd year, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.50,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Best time of your life.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.06,0:13:24.73,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,It's basic human kindness not to want to separate good friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.13,0:13:25.90,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Kindness?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.90,0:13:30.57,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So some handsome teacher suggested.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.99,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Handsome?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.68,0:13:38.96,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,After 1st year, it's easy to tell who the \Ngood friends and not so good friends are.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.61,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't even homeroom teacher for the whole—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.61,0:13:46.97,Alt,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,That handsome teacher's name was Kazuichi Arai.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.30,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,The man who will one day become president!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.94,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.94,0:13:55.53,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of time and chocolate.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.85,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are good friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.69,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good time together while you're here.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.98,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,His existence is a miracle.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.70,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird to hear that after hearing him brag about himself first.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.14,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.38,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.84,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.43,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.61,0:15:02.74,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite popular after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait! Do you already have someone you like?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.51,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You do, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.39,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about personal privacy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.04,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.38,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,If it's someone I know, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.50,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Yano.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need help.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.48,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.73,0:15:34.67,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you, Yano. I'd want to tell the person \Nwho I like first before I tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.00,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't work at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.46,0:15:46.20,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's the type who doesn't \Nlike it when others try to interfere.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.20,0:15:50.80,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it is something that the parties \Nin question should take care of themselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.37,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to hold myself back
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.21,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,unless the timing doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.86,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This corner will be for medicinal plants!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-A witch?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.69,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.17,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that he'd still be here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You planted a lot of seeds.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.08,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.18,0:16:59.38,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he'd already gone home.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.68,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.31,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.74,0:17:12.41,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.37,0:17:19.26,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what am I supposed to do when this happens?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.90,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.68,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.47,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He laughed.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.26,0:17:41.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't talk as much because our seats are farther apart now.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.76,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.78,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Was he... worried about me?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.42,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together until graduation now.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.42,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.86,0:18:00.98,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me even happier.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.81,0:18:07.05,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me so happy that Kazehaya and I \Ncan be in the same class until graduation.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.95,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And it makes me want to be with him even more.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.95,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Were you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.54,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.49,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.06,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.17,0:18:42.70,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I considered myself the closest to you out of all of the guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was too conceited.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.13,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Closest...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.10,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.12,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.84,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to put you in an awkward \Nposition by saying that suddenly.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.06,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.12,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.76,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.92,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.14,0:20:24.73,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that there was nothing I could \Nsay that wouldn't mean something special.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.23,Default,Kento,0000,0000,0000,,That's an unexpected combination.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.15,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,A smile that captured everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.20,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,The way it was before.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.80,0:22:33.80,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Forget.
